import React from "react"
import * as Mui from "@mui/material"
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"

function Navbar({handleLogout}) {
    return(
        <Mui.Box>
            <Mui.AppBar sx={{position: "static"}}>
            <Link to="">
                <Mui.Typography sx={{minWidth: 100}}>Home</Mui.Typography>
                </Link>
                {
                    localStorage.hasOwnProperty('token') && localStorage.hasOwnProperty('userData') ? 
                    <Link to="/logout">
                    <Mui.Typography sx={{minWidth: 100}}>Logout</Mui.Typography>
                    </Link>
                    :
                    <>
                    <Link to="/login">
                    <Mui.Typography sx={{minWidth: 100}}>Login</Mui.Typography>
                    </Link>
                    <Link to="/register">
                    <Mui.Typography sx={{minWidth: 100}}>Register</Mui.Typography>
                    </Link>
                    </>
                }
            </Mui.AppBar>
        </Mui.Box>
    )

}

export default Navbar
